{"tid":377043,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Kerbal Space Program有冇巴打玩/玩過","createTime":"2017-08-27T12:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T12:36:15.000Z","uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cdef318b35854060185ae75009c711f1cc44a92","tid":377043,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"唔經唔覺放低左隻game年幾兩年<br />\n想知有冇巴打玩/玩過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 講左好多年既Multiplayer係唔係仲係未見影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後係KSP砌既stock part飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/v50vRzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv50vRzM.jpg&h=f3958053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SUnUjsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSUnUjsG.jpg&h=38d24423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3XSdvL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3XSdvL3.jpg&h=7441f94d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b8f6466aed4e4ff5c30dd3ce3ba42e97e3564dd","tid":377043,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"唔係太空game咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜留係大氣層入面飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8d1b40482751b8bdc7900ca2b78c85a5b03ff5","tid":377043,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"係囉 我果時係砌火箭"},{"pid":"f9d1a00481b87ab263c98138352b360e415b0317","tid":377043,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"同埋有好多mod都冇更新<br />\nsteam又強制更新隻game<br />\n搞到冇得用舊mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b540a1ce759e50c73a186cb103ce085f9fd226c0","tid":377043,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係囉 我果時係砌火箭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地係SSTO黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iHIJ1vA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiHIJ1vA.jpg&h=2eb32fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度係Laythe<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/g36gZAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fg36gZAR.jpg&h=32a00103&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba1a35942362f2d49b77a10defd85e62d4279eb9","tid":377043,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋有好多mod都冇更新<br />\nsteam又強制更新隻game<br />\n搞到冇得用舊mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝太多mod一更新就奶晒野<br />\n好易壞save <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ea578bd136f2843d5a9faa4cb4d0de73db3901","tid":377043,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋有好多mod都冇更新<br />\nsteam又強制更新隻game<br />\n搞到冇得用舊mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝太多mod一更新就奶晒野<br />\n好易壞save <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要幾個大mod<br />\nUKS，KPBS，KIS，KAS，mechjeb，HyperEdit<br />\n仲有啲microwave power<br />\n可以reconfig嘅storage<br />\n穿梭機之前舊版有mark IV<br />\n但個mod主已經冇再更新<br />\n<br />\nUKS唔知係唔係簡化咗，好多Duna建築唔見晒，個StarLifter得返6樣嘢，我記得以前都好似要搞下個community category先出返晒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願返去玩個舊版算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b91fc286c6087fbfd10ac5768145b051bf78b6","tid":377043,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋有好多mod都冇更新<br />\nsteam又強制更新隻game<br />\n搞到冇得用舊mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝太多mod一更新就奶晒野<br />\n好易壞save <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要幾個大mod<br />\nUKS，KPBS，KIS，KAS，mechjeb，HyperEdit<br />\n仲有啲microwave power<br />\n可以reconfig嘅storage<br />\n穿梭機之前舊版有mark IV<br />\n但個mod主已經冇再更新<br />\n<br />\nUKS唔知係唔係簡化咗，好多Duna建築唔見晒，個StarLifter得返6樣嘢，我記得以前都好似要搞下個community category先出返晒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願返去玩個舊版算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞咗幾日，新版都係用唔返UKS以前OKS嗰部份建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇外國forum，mod主話唔會再有OKS，會用其他新嘢代替<br />\n佢究竟有冇諗過會令到用開佢個mod嘅玩家炒save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊版帶過嚟個save，由17 vessels炒到得返2 vessels<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsave低嘅craft templates全部都用唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf7d47a2e75cad26100473295e3ba1a2beef966","tid":377043,"uid":144126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:02:16.000Z","msg":"對spacecraft geek 嚟個game真係極品<br />\n遲吓出historical pack可以重現太空競賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919d6522d2aa9c9451e8bdd3c8dda20fbf46eb3e","tid":377043,"uid":79164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:09:24.000Z","msg":"買左未玩，巴打咁有心機砌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d00aa8f7c8b7dbb852db9a073fd9eebe214a90","tid":377043,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋有好多mod都冇更新<br />\nsteam又強制更新隻game<br />\n搞到冇得用舊mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝太多mod一更新就奶晒野<br />\n好易壞save <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要幾個大mod<br />\nUKS，KPBS，KIS，KAS，mechjeb，HyperEdit<br />\n仲有啲microwave power<br />\n可以reconfig嘅storage<br />\n穿梭機之前舊版有mark IV<br />\n但個mod主已經冇再更新<br />\n<br />\nUKS唔知係唔係簡化咗，好多Duna建築唔見晒，個StarLifter得返6樣嘢，我記得以前都好似要搞下個community category先出返晒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願返去玩個舊版算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我堅持用stock part唔用mod既part<br />\n至少唔會炒晒成個save或者craft檔"},{"pid":"01111e9ca87c23bd956e2ddf6604a91929184a73","tid":377043,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左未玩，巴打咁有心機砌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nKSP難上手，但係上到手明晒個原理<br />\n全部玩法都大同小異，變化又多<br />\n<br />\n如果出到multiplayer真係有排玩"},{"pid":"65f2b16ba19510d4b692dab2107234c9fa9ba179","tid":377043,"uid":4198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"兩年前玩過 準備等出多d新野先玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實multiplayer一早有 不過唔係官方"},{"pid":"4ab9229edd6d1beee8672b372c8140c424675bc3","tid":377043,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩年前玩過 準備等出多d新野先玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實multiplayer一早有 不過唔係官方</blockquote><br />\n玩過mod既multiplayer，幾唔穩定<br />\n所以期待官方會出得更好<br />\n但而家仲未有消息"},{"pid":"b420d10c524d88c7517627102bfb199774752479","tid":377043,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋有好多mod都冇更新<br />\nsteam又強制更新隻game<br />\n搞到冇得用舊mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝太多mod一更新就奶晒野<br />\n好易壞save <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要幾個大mod<br />\nUKS，KPBS，KIS，KAS，mechjeb，HyperEdit<br />\n仲有啲microwave power<br />\n可以reconfig嘅storage<br />\n穿梭機之前舊版有mark IV<br />\n但個mod主已經冇再更新<br />\n<br />\nUKS唔知係唔係簡化咗，好多Duna建築唔見晒，個StarLifter得返6樣嘢，我記得以前都好似要搞下個community category先出返晒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願返去玩個舊版算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我堅持用stock part唔用mod既part<br />\n至少唔會炒晒成個save或者craft檔</blockquote><br />\n其實係USI比較麻煩，成日改嚟改去<br />\nKPBS個作者幾好，冇del嘢，佢個開放式基地系統，可以方便加新嘢去同其他mod兼容<br />\n玩過mod真係好難返轉頭，特別係玩生理需要同殖民基地"},{"pid":"96eceb742a7a0f85a0cfe7b2d30914ac9943a8ab","tid":377043,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"幾年前玩過 依家多左咩新野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5240b6a1b28dc0457a085e4f1ce65d171776d794","tid":377043,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前玩過 依家多左咩新野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n將之前部份係mod嘅嘢拼咗入stock<br />\nrelay antenna，ISRU converter<br />\n其他大致相同<br />\nmod就視乎你玩開邊款，USI大執過，冇晒OKS嘅嘢"}]}